## Additional Information

### Project: Hook Lab
**Description**: A comprehensive React Hooks learning platform built with Next.js 15, featuring interactive examples and detailed explanations of React Hooks.

**Author**: Munya  
**Email**: syntaxread3r@gmail.com  
**GitHub**: https://github.com/syntax-read3r/hook-lab  
**Live Demo**: https://syntax-read3r.github.io/hook-lab/

